cle cx="12" cy="12" r="1"></circle><circle cx="19" cy="12" r="1"></circle><circle cx="5" cy="12" r="1"></circle></svg></span></button></div></div><div style="height: 1px; position: absolute; bottom: 0px; z-index: 1000;"></div></div><div class="relative group flex flex-col justify-center w-full max-w-[var(--content-max-width)] pb-0.5 items-end" id="response-a007ad46-aee2-4cfd-ba1c-8b618861be6a" style="scroll-margin-top: var(--scroll-margin-top, 0px);"><div dir="auto" class="message-bubble relative rounded-3xl text-primary min-h-7 prose dark:prose-invert break-words prose-p:opacity-100 prose-strong:opacity-100 prose-li:opacity-100 prose-ul:opacity-100 prose-ol:opacity-100 prose-ul:my-1 prose-ol:my-1 prose-li:my-2 last:prose-li:mb-3 prose-li:ps-1 prose-li:ms-1 bg-surface-l1 border border-border-l1 max-w-[100%] @sm/mainview:max-w-[90%] px-4 rounded-br-lg"><div class="relative"><div class="relative response-content-markdown markdown [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose)]:text-current [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose):hover]:text-primary [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose):hover]:decoration-primary [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose)]:underline [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose)]:decoration-primary/30 [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose)]:underline-offset-2 [&amp;_h2:not(.not-prose):first-child]:mt-0 [&amp;_h3:not(.not-prose):first-child]:mt-0 [&amp;_h4:not(.not-prose):first-child]:mt-0"><p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">#!/usr/bin/env bash</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words"># sp-hollywood ŌĆö Spherepop cinematic console</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words"># Adds: conference-demo, reviewer-mode, boss key, screensaver, fake logs, crash-theater</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">set -euo pipefail</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">PKG="sp-hollywood"
BASE_DIR="<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">"</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(cd "</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">c</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord">"</span></span></span></span>(dirname "$0")/.." &amp;&amp; pwd)"
WIDGET_DIR="$BASE_DIR/lib/spherepop/widgets"
LOGFILE="${SP_LOGFILE:-/tmp/spherepop.log}"</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">SPLITS=9
DELAY=15
MODE="normal"
BOSS_TITLE="build-env"
SCREENSAVER=0</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">trap 'tmux kill-session -t "$PKG" &gt;/dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1 || true; exit 0' INT TERM</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">usage() {
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cat &lt;&lt;'EOF'
sp-hollywood ŌĆö Spherepop cinematic console</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Modes:
&nbsp;&nbsp;--conference-demo   Fast, loud, pane-heavy demo mode
&nbsp;&nbsp;--reviewer-mode     Slow, legible, citation-ish mode
&nbsp;&nbsp;--boss              Start directly in boss-safe screen
&nbsp;&nbsp;--screensaver       Ignore keys; drift forever (best for projector)</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Options:
&nbsp;&nbsp;-s, --splits N      Max panes (default varies by mode)
&nbsp;&nbsp;-d, --delay  N      Pane rotation interval seconds
&nbsp;&nbsp;--logfile PATH      Where to write fake logs (default: /tmp/spherepop.log)
&nbsp;&nbsp;-h, --help          Help</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Runtime (tmux):
&nbsp;&nbsp;Ctrl-B + B          Boss key (instant safe screen)
&nbsp;&nbsp;Ctrl-B + R          Reviewer mode toggle
&nbsp;&nbsp;Ctrl-B + D          Demo mode toggle
EOF
}</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words"># ---------- mode presets ----------</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">preset_conference() { MODE="conference"; SPLITS=<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>S</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>L</mi><mi>I</mi><mi>T</mi><mi>S</mi><mo>:</mo><mo>ŌłÆ</mo><mn>14</mn></mrow><mo separator="true">;</mo><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi><mi>L</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>Y</mi><mo>=</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{SPLITS:-14}; DELAY=</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.8778em; vertical-align: -0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.13889em;">SP</span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.05764em;">TS</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">:</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mord">ŌłÆ</span><span class="mord">14</span></span><span class="mpunct">;</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.05764em;">E</span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.22222em;">Y</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span></span></span></span>{DELAY:-6}; }
preset_reviewer()    { MODE="reviewer";    SPLITS=<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>S</mi><mi>P</mi><mi>L</mi><mi>I</mi><mi>T</mi><mi>S</mi><mo>:</mo><mo>ŌłÆ</mo><mn>7</mn></mrow><mo separator="true">;</mo><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi><mi>L</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>Y</mi><mo>=</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{SPLITS:-7};  DELAY=</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.8778em; vertical-align: -0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.13889em;">SP</span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.05764em;">TS</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">:</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mord">ŌłÆ</span><span class="mord">7</span></span><span class="mpunct">;</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.05764em;">E</span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.22222em;">Y</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span></span></span></span>{DELAY:-20}; }</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words"># ---------- widgets ----------</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">pick_widget() { ls "$WIDGET_DIR" 2&gt;/dev/null | sort -R | head -n1; }</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">spin_up() {
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;local dir="-v" panes splits pane count=0 w
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for w in $(ls "$WIDGET_DIR" 2&gt;/dev/null | sort -R); do
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[ "$dir" = "-v" ] &amp;&amp; dir="-h" || dir="-v"
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;panes=$(tmux list-panes -t "$PKG" 2&gt;/dev/null || true)
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;splits=$(echo "$panes" | wc -l | tr -d ' ')
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[ "$splits" -eq 0 ] &amp;&amp; break
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pane=$((RANDOM % splits))</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;tmux split-window <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>r</mi><mo>ŌłÆ</mo><mi>t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">"</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">dir -t "</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.7778em; vertical-align: -0.0833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">ŌłÆ</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mord">"</span></span></span></span>{PKG}.$pane" 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"nice -n 19 bash '$WIDGET_DIR/$w' '$MODE' '$LOGFILE'" 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;/dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1 || true</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sleep 0.15
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;count=$((count + 1))
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[ "$count" -ge "$SPLITS" ] &amp;&amp; break
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;done</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;tmux select-layout tiled &gt;/dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1 || true
}</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">boss_key() {
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;tmux rename-window "$BOSS_TITLE"
