<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Key enhancements observed include:</p>
<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary" node="[object Object]">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal" node="[object Object]"><strong class="font-semibold" node="[object Object]">Mode-specific behaviors</strong>: The conference-demo mode emphasizes rapid, high-density pane rotation with occasional alerts, suitable for dynamic presentations. The reviewer-mode prioritizes slower cycles, fewer panes, and legible displays with philosophical citations, facilitating thoughtful discussion.</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal" node="[object Object]"><strong class="font-semibold" node="[object Object]">Screensaver functionality</strong>: This option minimizes interactivity, ideal for passive display on projectors.</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal" node="[object Object]"><strong class="font-semibold" node="[object Object]">Boss key integration</strong>: A rapid switch to innocuous system monitoring and documentation panes enhances practicality in professional settings.</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal" node="[object Object]"><strong class="font-semibold" node="[object Object]">Widget ecosystem</strong>: The modular widgets (e.g., fake log generation, status monitoring, and theatrical "crash" simulations) ensure harmless yet convincing activity, with thematic elements like metric instability and invariant checks.</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal" node="[object Object]"><strong class="font-semibold" node="[object Object]">Supporting tools</strong>: The man page, build script, and log seeding utility contribute to a complete, polished package.</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Overall, the script effectively stages "epistemic theater" around topics in AI safety and theory without implying operational capabilities, aligning with its stated intent for demos.</p>
