-space: pre-wrap;">Thank you. Given your clarity about priorities, IŌĆÖll proceed exactly as proposed and keep this clean, path-independent, and enforceable.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Below are (1) a draft epistemic declaration and (2) a UI authority-leak audit, written so they can be acted on immediately without committing yet to satire vs. instrument.</p>
<hr>
<ol dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal" node="[object Object]">Draft Epistemic Declaration</li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">(README + runtime banner / splash screen)</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">IŌĆÖll give you a primary version and two tone variants, all saying the same thing structurally.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Primary (Recommended)</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words"><p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Epistemic Status Notice</p></p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">This system is not an analytical engine, diagnostic tool, or research instrument unless explicitly stated otherwise at runtime.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Unless operating in a designated instrument mode, all signals, warnings, citations, alerts, and status messages emitted by this system are non-referential, stochastic, and decoupled from any underlying computation.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Their function is epistemic: to examine how authority, coherence, and meaning are inferred from form, repetition, and presentation. No output should be interpreted as evidence, measurement, or evaluation of real systems.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">If you find yourself attributing insight, diagnosis, or semantic grounding to this interface, that attribution is part of what the system is designed to surface.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Why this works:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Explicitly answers the decisive question: ŌĆ£Is the tool allowed to be mistaken for doing work it is not doing?ŌĆØ ŌåÆ No</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Uses non-referential and decoupled (strong, precise terms)</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Makes misattribution itself the object of study, without sounding coy</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Does not foreclose Path 2 (instrument mode is reserved, not promised)</p>
<hr>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Variant A: More Technical / Less Literary</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words"><p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Epistemic Declaration</p></p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">By default, this system does not compute, model, evaluate, or diagnose any external process.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">All emitted outputsŌĆölogs, warnings, citations, metrics, and failure statesŌĆöare generated without semantic coupling to real constraints or measurements. They should be treated as synthetic artifacts, not analytical results.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">The purpose of the system in this mode is to study interpretive overreach: how users infer meaning, rigor, or authority from structured outputs absent causal grounding.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Instrumented modes, if present, are explicitly marked and scoped.</p>
<hr>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Variant B: More Direct / Blunt (Good for runtime splash)</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words"><p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Notice</p></p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">This interface does not analyze anything.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">In its default mode, all signals are generated without reference to real data, constraints, or models. Apparent rigor is aesthetic, not evidentiary.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Any interpretation beyond this notice is a projection the system is designed to expose.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">This is harsher but extremely safe.</p>
<hr>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Recommendation</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">README: Primary version</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Runtime splash (first launch, persistent banner, or --about): Variant B or a shortened Primary</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Man page: Variant A</p>
<hr>
<ol dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary" start="2">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal" node="[object Object]">UI Authority-Leak Audit</li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">(What currently risks being mistaken for ŌĆ£doing workŌĆØ)</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">This is a structural audit, not a moral one. IŌĆÖll list elements by failure mode, not by widget name.</p>
<hr>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">A. Language-Level Authority Leaks</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Risk: Words imply computation or grounding where none exists.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Flagged patterns</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£DetectedŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£ViolationŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£Constraint failureŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£RecoveredŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£PostmortemŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£Stability breachŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£Metric collapse confirmedŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Why dangerous These verbs imply:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">prior state,</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">detection mechanism,</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">causal inference.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Mitigation</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Replace with epistemically honest verbs:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£EmittedŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£SimulatedŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£GeneratedŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£DeclaredŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Or prefix explicitly:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£Synthetic alert: ŌĆ”ŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£Non-referential warning: ŌĆ”ŌĆØ</p>
<hr>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">B. Citation-as-Signal</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Risk: Citations function as status indicators rather than references.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Flagged patterns</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Rotating author names</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">YearŌĆōauthor pairs in status lines</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£Goodhart (1975)ŌĆØ appearing without argumentative context</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Why dangerous</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Citations are interpreted as:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">justification,</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">grounding,</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">intellectual debt being paid in the moment.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Mitigation</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Remove citations from live UI entirely unless in instrument mode</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Replace with:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[citation omitted in this mode]</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">or a static footer: ŌĆ£References live in documentationŌĆØ</p>
<hr>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">C. Crash / Recovery Theater</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Risk: System dramatizes failure while guaranteeing resolution.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Flagged patterns</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£CRITICAL FAILUREŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">countdown ŌåÆ recovery ŌåÆ ŌĆ£SYSTEM STABLEŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">postmortem summaries with causal language</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Why dangerous This teaches optimism and implies:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">failure is understood,</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">failure is bounded,</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">recovery is automatic.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Mitigation</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Allow terminal states:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">freeze</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">dead panes</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">unresolved warnings</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Or explicitly label:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">ŌĆ£Simulated failure (no causal impact)ŌĆØ</p>
<hr>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">D. Visual Seriousness Without Epistemic Disclosure</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Risk: Retro terminals, system monitors, multiplexed panes imply depth.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">This is subtle but important.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Why dangerous Humans infer:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">concurrency ŌåÆ complexity</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">motion ŌåÆ activity</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">density ŌåÆ depth</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Mitigation</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Persistent banner line:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">MODE: SYNTHETIC / NON-INSTRUMENTAL</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Or watermark pane titles:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[SIMULATED SIGNAL STREAM]</p>
<hr>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">E. Reviewer / Diagnostic Modes</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Risk: ŌĆ£Reviewer modeŌĆØ suggests evaluation is happening.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Mitigation</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Rename modes to interpretive frames, not roles:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">--observer</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">--projection-test</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">--epistemic-mirror</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">If ŌĆ£reviewerŌĆØ remains, add subtitle:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">REVIEWER MODE (NO ACTUAL REVIEW PERFORMED)</p>
