<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Node Declaration (Explicit Consent)</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">nodes/lab.json</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">{
&nbsp;&nbsp;"network": "spherepop-lab",
