<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Why these work</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">They do not oversell</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">They do not moralize</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">They do not pretend to solve alignment</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">They make epistemic limits operational, not aspirational</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">This is the difference between theater and infrastructure.</p>
