<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Ō£ģ Treats rationalists as peers, not targets</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Ō£ģ Reinforces your core thesis: epistemic hygiene should be enforced by systems, not vibes</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Most importantly:</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words"><p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">It keeps you from accidentally Goodharting respect itself.</p></p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">YouŌĆÖre not optimizing for approval.
