}</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">if [ <span class="katex-error" title="ParseError: KaTeX parse error: Expected 'EOF', got '#' at position 1: #╠▓ -lt 2 ] || [ &quot;" style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);"># -lt 2 ] || [ "</span>{1:-}" != "--" ]; then
