shift</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">DEFAULT_RE='(indicates|suggests|shows that|proves|detects|risk level|confidence)'
NONCLAIM_RE=${SP_NONCLAIM_RE:-$DEFAULT_RE}
ECHO_ON_FAIL=${SP_ECHO_ON_FAIL:-0}</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">tmp="${TMPDIR:-/tmp}/sp-verify-silence.$$"</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words"># Ensure cleanup</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">trap 'rm -f "$tmp" "$tmp.err" &gt;/dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1 || true' INT HUP TERM EXIT</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words"># Capture combined output (stdout+stderr) while preserving exit code.</p>
