<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">WhatŌĆÖs ŌĆ£weirdŌĆØ here isnŌĆÖt accidental; itŌĆÖs a structural inversion thatŌĆÖs worth naming clearly.</p>
